paragraph
 Red is a computer programming language. Red was made to overcome the limitations of the programming language Rebol. Introduced in 2011 by Nenad Rakocevic, Red is both an imperative and functional programming language. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_(programming_language)">Read more on Wikipedia...</a>

